rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nThe Left throw eggs: Justice, Hero<br />\n<br />\nThe Right throw eggs: Fascist, Violent<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母白皮豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6d00b1770c6e72c0773893e1f85decf44848f23","tid":1066650,"uid":170229,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"05d0d933c10be2973c6dfcb16504bb34dfa856b5","tid":1066650,"uid":9053,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:32:17.000Z","msg":"澳洲參議員安寧（Fraser Anning，圖左）前日把新西蘭槍擊案襲歸咎於穆斯林移民政策後，遭一名17歲少年（圖右）在他頭上敲破雞蛋；安寧隨即揮拳還擊。澳洲跨黨派議員皆譴責安寧的舉動，總理莫理森更向記者指，會動用「法律所有力量」對付安寧。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係睇唔透呢個世界"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hCDYi36.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhCDYi36.png&h=de9a36c5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rqONcpa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrqONcpa.png&h=54bba8c4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7489b78341fb15eead421bb6b15d755e37f1dfa1","tid":1066650,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ccad21df0c9ce6f4ba5295be7d92ab6ff03d13","tid":1066650,"uid":82301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1880b8cea64de45b2440e2779170ac0df379904e","tid":1066650,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"比人襲擊唔還得手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"冇話唔得<br />\n唔好睇囉<br />\npublic figure咁易開拖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zw97LIBGbR4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dzw97LIBGbR4&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4MwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=519d9d38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zw97LIBGbR4</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"你唔鐘意咪下次唔選或動議dq佢囉，冇話唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9493a103943da28bfe97584cde722badd9b762cb","tid":1066650,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7489b78341fb15eead421bb6b15d755e37f1dfa1","tid":1066650,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1ccad21df0c9ce6f4ba5295be7d92ab6ff03d13","tid":1066650,"uid":82301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1880b8cea64de45b2440e2779170ac0df379904e","tid":1066650,"uid":64009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"比人襲擊唔還得手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T05:48:11.000Z","msg":"冇話唔得<br />\n唔好睇囉<br />\npublic figure咁易開拖<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zw97LIBGbR4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dzw97LIBGbR4&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4MwAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=519d9d38\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zw97LIBGbR4</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T06:27:48.000Z","msg":"你唔鐘意咪下次唔選或動議dq佢囉，冇話唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:12:38.000Z","msg":"Senator Anning's comments from Friday have prompted a petition, which has so far attracted more than a million signatures, calling for him to be removed from parliament.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Everyone is entitled to their opinion,&quot; he said.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;A million people from Australia &mdash; I am not sure they are all from Australia &mdash; but yes, a million have signed the petition, however quite a lot of people have told us they're happy for me to stay where I'm at.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe houses of Parliament are unable to expel a politician for their behaviour, but an MP or senator can be expelled if they are convicted of an offence punishable by imprisonment for a year or longer.<br />\n<br />\nThe Government and Opposition will join forces to censure him when parliament resumes next month."},{"pid":"51a31b91e9d06bf39339eece7e51fea63caa4e8b","tid":1066650,"uid":88304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}